<pb facs="1079207" n="1"/>
<opener><salute>Viro Illustrissimo et Celeberrimo <choice><abbr>Jo:</abbr><expan>Johanni</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoullio</rs>
<lb/>Petrus Antonius <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelottus</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Quam s<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>pius pollicitus sum Dissertationem
         <lb/><rs key="biblio_M3G2JA79" type="biblio">de Separatione Fluidorum in Corpore Animali</rs><note type="editorial">Michelotti, Pietro Antonio, De separatione fluidorum in corpore animali dissertatio physico-mechanico-medica, Venetiis (A. &amp; A. Pinelli) 1721. (Digitalisat bei BSB digital). Bibliographie zur Korrespondenz zwischen Johann I Bernoulli und Johann Jakob Scheuchzer.</note>
<lb/>una cum nova pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stantissimarum Tuarum
         <lb/><rs key="biblio_JAFFCHKU" type="biblio">de Motu Musculor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>, ac <rs key="biblio_W6BHQDM2" type="biblio">de Effer<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>vescentia, et Fermentatione</rs> Disser<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tationum editione, tandem ad Te, Vir Nobi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>lissime, mitto tanquam summ<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Observanti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> er<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>ga Te me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> testem. Perlibenter ex <rs key="brieftag" type="letter">Literis</rs><note type="editorial">Meint Bernoullis Antwort, die erst noch kommt. Identifizieren oder ref streichen.<!-- Der letzte Brief 000056706 von Joh. I Bernoulli an Michelotti ist vom 10. August 1720. Allerdings geht es dort weniger um positive Rückmeldung seitens Joh. I Bernoullis zu den Anmerkungen zu seinen Dissertationen, als darum, dass er sich über die Portoverschwendung wegen unnötige langen und vielen Briefen echauffiert. --></note> Tuis in<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>telligam num Tibi placeant ea, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tuo permissu
         <lb/>in illis ipsis Tuis eximiis <rs key="biblio_W6BHQDM2 biblio_JAFFCHKU" type="biblios">Dissertationibus</rs>, ad cer<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tas quasdam Latinas voces pertinentia mutavi,
         <lb/>uti etiam si Tibi arrideant X, quas videbis Ani<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>madversiones, ad ea, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><abbr>Ja.</abbr><expan>Jacobus</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1055365613" type="person">Keillius</rs> proposuit in <rs key="biblio_WCRRQGZT" type="biblio">Ten<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tamine</rs><note type="editorial">Keill, James, De motu musculari, in: Tentamina Medico-Physica, London (G. Strahan) 1718, pp. 131-149. Bibliographie zur Korrespondenz zwischen Johann I Bernoulli und Johann Jakob Scheuchzer.</note> Physico-Medico, quod est de Motu Musculari.
         <lb/>Rogo ut legere digneris etiam Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>fation<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>, quam Tuis
         <lb/><rs key="biblio_W6BHQDM2 biblio_JAFFCHKU" type="biblios">Dissertationibus</rs> modo memoratis pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>misi. Ceter<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
         <lb/>quum duo ad Te exemplaria mittere sta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tuerim pergrat<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> mihi feceris, si eor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> alter<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>clarissimo Agnato Tuo <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao</rs> meo nomine
       <pb facs="1079208" n="2"/>
<lb/>donaveris eundemque salutaveris. Misiss<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> tertium
         <lb/>exemplar ad Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stantissim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Fili<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Danielem</rs>,
         <lb/>si Clarissimus <rs key="pers_DE-588-117260266" type="person">Sterlinus</rs> id ferre potuisset. Dic ergo
         <lb/>ipsi Clarissimo <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Filio</rs> Tuo, meo nomine salutem
         <lb/>plurimam, rogaque ut mihi parcat, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice>d nond<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/><choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> respons<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> dederim ad doctissimam <rs key="brieftag" type="letter">epistol<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice></rs><note type="editorial">Dieser Brief von Daniel I an Michelotti scheint nicht überliefert.</note>,
         <lb/>quam ante multos menses ad me dedit. Responde<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>bo quamprimum. Interim dic illi, me esse paratissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>m<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> ad ips<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> in Dom<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> me<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> recipiend<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>. Certe
         <lb/>si advenerit, uti spero, domi me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> permanebit, ipsi
         <lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>bebo quotidie occasion<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> videndi meos <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>gro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tos, ipsi meos libros offeram cujusquemodi generis,
         <lb/>eritque meus condiscipulus, immovero e<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> loco
         <lb/>Filii habebo.</p> <closer><salute>Vale, Vir Amicissime, et fave.</salute> <dateline><choice><abbr>D.</abbr><expan>Dabam</expan></choice> <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Vene<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> <date when="1721-04-12">12<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> Aprilis 1721.</date></dateline></closer>
